 Flow 
 1)pehle hamare index.js file me jayenge waha hoga
     <BrowserRouter>
        <Provider store={store}>
          <App />   
          <Toaster/>  
        </Provider>
    </BrowserRouter>

  yaha BrowserRouter use hua hai for making Routes and Provider use hua hai for redux  
   
 2) App component  pehle use kiya hai for rendering first component of App
 
 3)App me jayenge waha hamare pass hai
  1)Navbar
  2)Routes

4)Now , hum jayenge navbar me waha required work karenge then

5)Routes me jo component hai 
  1)home
  2)cart
  
6)home page component me jaake required work karenge (for ex => get fake data from api calling , or storing all the data in posts)

7)mai post ko as a card dekhna chahta hu and saara ka saara data in the form of array hai isliye , we'll use map fun

8)Now in product component , do required work

9)Now in spinner

10) Now in Cart =>in cart we have two types of data 
1)show all the items
2)show the summary
we can do that by getting the data of cart but it is in slice so we used useSelector()
